      "Turn one exact source passage already selected as evidence in a Scient project into a concise, editable note proposal linked to that selection. Use when the researcher wants to preserve what the passage contributes, such as a result, method, limitation, definition, argument, or attributed interpretation. Do not use to capture evidence, summarize an entire source, add independent analysis, combine evidence selections, audit claims, or draft manuscript text.",
